            drywall replacement due to extensive water damage or foundation
            settlement can run <strong>$1,000-$3,000+</strong>. Here's our
            professional opinion: Don't wait on small cracks—foundation movement
            in North Texas clay soil means they'll only get worse. The $100
            repair today could prevent a $2,000 replacement later. We provide
